data.description: Experience the harmony of design and comfort in this 3-bed, 2-bath home on a coveted corner lot with RV Gate Space ! The living room welcomes you with its neutral palette, abundant natural light, and sleek tile flooring, crafting an ambiance of warmth and elegance. The eat-in kitchen boasts track and recessed lighting, paneled cabinets, SS appliances, a pantry, and sliding doors leading to the backyard, effortlessly merging indoor-outdoor living. Retreat to the cozy main bedroom, featuring plush carpeting, a walk-in closet, and a private bathroom with dual sinks. The expansive backyard holds limitless potential: a patio perfect for lounging, a handy storage shed, picturesque mountain views, and ample space waiting to be transformed into your dream oasis.
